            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌192點  航空股插水  消費股捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股全日跌192點，開市已為全日高位，美國郵政宣布暫停收中港包裹，電商及航空股受壓，消費股弱，聯想(00992)跑贏，航運股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收報20597，跌192點或0.93%，今早開市報20827點，升37點或0.18%，已為全日高位，早段低見20417，跌372點或1.79%，為全日低位，午後一度跌逾250點，惟波幅不超過上午。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-113558_source-web_00753.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-113558_source-web_00753.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：國航官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135718_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135718_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240710_FI_source-web_09633-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240710_FI_source-web_09633-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-113558_source-web_00753.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：國航官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135718_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240710_FI_source-web_09633-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報4930，跌47點或0.95% ; 今早開報4975點，跌1點或0.03%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報7566，跌77點或1.01% ; 今早以7652點開市，升8點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報20648，跌192點或0.92%，高水51點 ; 科指期貨全日跌40點或0.8%，報4945點，高水15點 ; 國指期貨全日報7578，跌94點或1.23%，高水12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市全日成交1922.11億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國郵政即日起暫停接收來自中國內地和香港包裹，較早前公布取消了價值低於800美元的「小額豁免」條款。此外周二正式啟動對中國進口商品加徵10%關稅的行動。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相關股份偏軟，兩大中資電商股阿里巴巴(09988)跌0.1%，報97.55元 ; 京東(09618)挫3.46%，報156.5元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">貨運量受惠於跨國電商的國泰航空(00293)收跌3.26%，報10.1元 ; 其他航空股也捱沽，中國國航(00753)瀉4.4%，報4.56元；南方航空(01055)跌3.31%，報3.51元；東方航空(00670)跌2.85%，報2.39元，同系A股上市的東航物流(601156.SH)更插10.01%跌停板，報14.75元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">順豐(06936)收市跌幅收窄至0.15%，報33.25元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-113558_source-web_00753.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-113558_source-web_00753.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：國航官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">近日受惠Deepseek概念強勢的AI概念股回吐，金山雲(03896)收跌4.43%，報8.2元 ; 第四範式(06682)曾插13.27%，低見54.25元，收瀉9.91%，報56.35元 ; 商湯 (00020)跌4.62%，報1.65元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">惟聯想(00992)內地GPU獨角獸沐曦發布Deepseek一體機解決方案，摩根士丹利評為「增持」，目標價13.8元。聯想全日跑贏，收升3.99%，報10.94元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135718_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135718_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙證稱內地消費仍疲軟 調低多股目標價，內需消費股午後進一步下跌，農夫山泉(09633)挫6.94%，報34.85元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 攜程(09961)報534元，跌6.4% ; 蒙牛乳業(02319)報14.98元，跌4.59% ; 海底撈(06862)報14.42元，跌3.61% ;海爾智家(06690)報24.95元，跌3.48% ; 安踏(02020)跌3.41%，報82.25元 ; 華潤啤酒(00291)報23.55元，報2.89%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240710_FI_source-web_09633-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240710_FI_source-web_09633-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">航運股逆市升。中遠海能(01138)升5.76%，報7.89元，錄4連升，大摩發表策略報告，預期中遠海能未來15日內股價有約七至八成機會絕對值上升。目標價9.5元，評級「增持」。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東方海外(00316)升3.11%，報105.9元，升幅居藍籌股第二位 ; 中遠海控(01919)升2.62%，報11.74元 ;太平洋航運(02343)升2.45%，報1.67元。     波羅的海乾散貨指數(BDI)三連升，700點支持強；波羅的海原油運價指數(BDTI)連升，900點在望。  </p>\n</div>",
